### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Ahmad OnlineShop API — HTTP Test File
### Base URL: http://localhost:5141
### در Dev: OTP همیشه 00000 است
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5141
@apiVersion = 1
@api = {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### بعد از VerifyOtp این متغیر رو از response پر کن:
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@userId = 1
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 1 ─ ارسال OTP (بدون JWT)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/RequestOtp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "09121234567"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 2 ─ تأیید OTP → دریافت JWT  (در Dev کد: 00000)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/VerifyOtp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "09121234567",
  "code": "00000"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 3 ─ Refresh Token
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/RefreshToken
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken":  "{{token}}",
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 4 ─ Logout
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/Logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  USERS ─ مدیریت کاربران (نیاز به JWT دارد)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### لیست کاربران
GET {{api}}/Identity/Users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### دریافت کاربر با ID
GET {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### لیست نقش‌ها
GET {{api}}/Identity/Roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ویرایش پروفایل
PUT {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}/Profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fullName": "احمد حمیدی فرد"
}

###

### اختصاص نقش Seller (roleId=2)
POST {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}/Roles/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### حذف نقش Seller
DELETE {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}/Roles/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### فعال‌سازی کاربر
POST {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}/Activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### غیرفعال‌سازی کاربر
POST {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}/Deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### تعلیق کاربر
POST {{api}}/Identity/Users/{{userId}}/Suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  کاربران تست از Seed (همه OTP = 00000)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###
###  Admin    → 09000000001  (roleId=1)
###  Seller   → 09000000002  (roleId=2)
###  Customer → 09000000003  (roleId=3)
###

### ورود به عنوان Admin
POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/RequestOtp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "09000000001"
}

###

POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/VerifyOtp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "09000000001",
  "code": "00000"
}

###

### ورود به عنوان Seller
POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/VerifyOtp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "09000000002",
  "code": "00000"
}

###

### ورود به عنوان Customer
POST {{api}}/Identity/Auth/VerifyOtp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "09000000003",
  "code": "00000"
}

###
